        <h2>Why does it exist?</h2>
        <p>Our partner, <a href="http://www.giveforward.com/">GiveForward</a>, is providing a vital service by allowing people to create funding campaigns to pay for their loved ones' medical treatments. To date, more than $100 million has been given on the platform.</p>
        <p>Oftentimes, however, the campaigns never reach beyond friends, family, and other people specifically browsing GiveForward looking to make donations. While this is amazing in and of itself, many campaigns never reach their goal. Humanity Box's aim is to expose these campaigns to as many sites on the internet as possible. By increasing traffic to these campaigns we can help them get funded when they otherwise might not.</p>
